E

EdfExample - Class in example
This example program opens the EDF-file records/ekg.edf (that contains data from two measuring channels - cardiogram and accelerometer) and reads its records (one by one) and writes them to the new file ekgcopy1.bdf as it is reads data by samples (from both channels) and writes them to the new file ekgcopy2.bdf as it is does some filtering (that joins 10 data records first and then omits data from the first channel and averages samples from the second channel reducing the 50Hz noise) and writes the resultant records to ekgcopy3.bdf
